1
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,780
♪Trap my frame♪

2
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:20,060
♪Plagues demand I bow in shame♪

3
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,940
♪Snare my soul♪

4
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:27,100
♪Rules command I swallow my pride♪

5
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:30,620
♪Mock my way♪

6
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:34,060
♪Chained me where I must stay♪

7
00:00:34,420 --> 00:00:36,780
♪Taught me to kneel, not to speak♪

8
00:00:37,020 --> 00:00:41,220
♪And to let my life pass by in silence♪

9
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,100
♪But I heard the wind♪

10
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,900
♪From the sea and the sky♪

11
00:00:46,180 --> 00:00:47,660
♪It said don't bend♪

12
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,820
♪Bow your head, and your chains begin♪

13
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,380
♪You are the wave♪

14
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,300
♪And the wind that won't behave♪

15
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:56,340
♪How could you be chained?♪

16
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:58,740
♪Untamed, uncaged, unclaimed♪

17
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:00,540
♪You're the blade in my gaze♪

18
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:02,420
♪This world will leave you no space♪

19
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,220
♪Then pierce it with your blaze♪

20
00:01:04,220 --> 00:01:06,100
♪My silent grind♪

21
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:08,060
♪My aching pain♪

22
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,300
♪Will one day turn...♪

23
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:14,620
♪I am who I am♪

24
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:18,140
♪My greatest ambition♪

25
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:21,300
♪If the world can't contain me♪

26
00:01:21,380 --> 00:01:24,940
♪Then I'll break through it♪

27
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:26,940
♪Become who I am♪

28
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,260
[Wild Ambition Bloom]

29
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from Stone and Water's novel,
The Uncaged Flame]

30
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 27]

31
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:35,180
English prefixes have their rules.

32
00:01:35,790 --> 00:01:36,290
For example...

33
00:01:36,310 --> 00:01:38,260
And I know the meaning

34
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:41,180
of "come" and "go".

35
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,330
And?

36
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,050
Mommy, I love you!

37
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:46,540
Master these rules,

38
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,290
and you can memorize words effectively.

39
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:49,620
Thank you, Mr. Xia.

40
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:52,020
I'll dig into this later.

41
00:01:52,430 --> 00:01:53,930
Looking forward
to seeing you ace your next exam!

42
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:54,850
Absolutely!

43
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:55,770
Keep pushing!

44
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:02,820
What's wrong?

45
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,260
Nothing.

46
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,060
By the way,

47
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,450
how's your mother been lately?

48
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,540
She's in the hospital.

49
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,060
Is she ill?

50
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:20,690
No.

51
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,730
Just mad at me and Xia Yuan.

52
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,220
Because of me?

53
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:26,410
It has nothing to do with you.

54
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,730
She can't see things clearly.

55
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:32,980
Is there anything I can do?

56
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,220
Don't worry about it.

57
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,820
I understand her.

58
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,610
I've lost many loved ones.

59
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:46,610
I know that pain all too well.

60
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,260
So I hope

61
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:51,690
you won't let this

62
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:54,220
come between you and your family

63
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,340
because of me.

64
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,820
She's really upset right now.

65
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,850
I'm afraid no matter what you do,

66
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,690
it won't change her views on you.

67
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:07,060
Her views don't really matter.

68
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:09,850
What matters is as her son,

69
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,980
you should make her happy.

70
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:14,500
She has had

71
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,220
a really tough life.

72
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,220
Making her happy is simple.

73
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,290
Just obey her will.

74
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,220
But I won't compromise on this.

75
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,170
No, Xiao Chu.

76
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:31,450
I don't think

77
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:33,660
you understand her.

78
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,170
What she wants most

79
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:39,130
isn't your obedience.

80
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,660
Then what is it?

81
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:50,280
[Shanghai Hospital]

82
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,500
[VIP wards]
Shanghai Women's Federation

83
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,540
of All Sectors held
its second extraordinary meeting recently

84
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:56,850
and issued a declaration.

85
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:59,010
Is today the 17th?

86
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:00,260
Yes, it is.

87
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,170
Are you sure?

88
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:05,820
It reads here.

89
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:11,570
Shanghai Women's...

90
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:14,500
Seems they've forgotten me.

91
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:15,890
Forgotten what?

92
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,410
Shanghai Women's Federation of All Sectors

93
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,900
held its second...

94
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,490
Mother.

95
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,340
You're here!

96
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:27,490
Feeling better?

97
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:28,700
Much better!

98
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,250
Did you come alone?

99
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:36,170
Xia Yuan's been swamped lately.

100
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,140
Can't leave the shop.

101
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:38,490
What about Xia Chu?

102
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,140
Honestly,

103
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,250
I haven't seen him for days.

104
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,340
What about Youwen and Youze?

105
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:53,140
They're at school.

106
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:55,610
Forget it.

107
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,250
Can't count on anyone.

108
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:01,490
What's wrong? In a bad mood?

109
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,460
Nothing.

110
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,100
Let's go for a walk to cheer you up.

111
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:05,810
No.

112
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,930
You have to go.

113
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,170
The doctor told me

114
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,410
you have

115
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:12,410
a psychological issue,

116
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,410
so you need to go out for some air.

117
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,610
Look, what a lovely day!

118
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:17,900
Let's walk to refresh your mood.

119
00:05:18,070 --> 00:05:18,850
Let's go soak up some sunshine.

120
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,580
No.

121
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:20,660
I'm not going.

122
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,580
Go ahead, Mother.

123
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:22,340
Hurry up.

124
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,290
You're like a spoiled child.

125
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:27,610
Let's get some fresh air.

126
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,490
It'll help speed up your recovery.

127
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,370
Are you tired, Mother?

128
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,900
If you're tired, take a break anytime.

129
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,660
I'm not tired.

130
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,540
I was just wondering what day it is today.

131
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:40,020
Today is the 17th.

132
00:05:40,430 --> 00:05:42,370
What's special about the 17th?

133
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,250
Oh, no!

134
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:47,850
I forgot to settle the bill
with the tailor shop today!

135
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,250
I forgot it!

136
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:51,290
Enough!

137
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,050
Guess I put on this outfit for nothing.

138
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,220
I'll return and lie down on my deathbed.

139
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:54,850
Mother!

140
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:56,610
Look how nice you look in these!

141
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,020
It's such rare good weather.

142
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:58,730
Let's take a few more steps.

143
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,660
No.

144
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:02,460
Come on, just two more steps.

145
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,340
Let's go and see what's ahead.

146
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:06,980
Grandma's here.

147
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,730
- Grandma!
- Grandma!

148
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:12,020
Hello, Youwen, Youze.

149
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:12,850
Why are you…?

150
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,460
You two are also here?

151
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,340
Mother.

152
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,370
What on earth are you all doing?

153
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,580
Popping out one after another.

154
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,540
You'll see soon enough.

155
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:30,050
What are you doing?

156
00:06:30,070 --> 00:06:31,250
Why do you bring me here?

157
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:37,410
What's this?

158
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:40,100
Mother, they were invited
from our hometown

159
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,610
to perform
for your birthday celebration.

160
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,460
Hebei Bangzi Opera?

161
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:44,370
Yes.

162
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:45,930
To perform Hua Mulan?

163
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:46,930
Exactly!

164
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:49,810
Let the show begin now.

165
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,140
Please wait.

166
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:54,340
Why? Perform now!

167
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:56,580
The actress playing Hua Mulan

168
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:57,980
isn't ready yet.

169
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,290
Then...

170
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:03,100
Mother, we have gifts for you.

171
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,370
There are gifts?

172
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,780
Of course.

173
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,460
This…

174
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:20,980
Mother,

175
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,850
ever since I was little,

176
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:28,700
I knew you cherished such a complete set
of costumes.

177
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,220
I often saw you

178
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:32,810
take them out late at night

179
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,340
when no one else was around,

180
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,050
just gazing at them

181
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,700
and gently touching them.

182
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:41,250
Later when I started doing business

183
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:42,340
and needed capital,

184
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:45,050
you sold them without hesitation.

185
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,660
Is this my original set?

186
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,370
It was custom-made
based on your old photo

187
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,170
from back then.

188
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,730
How thoughtful and filial you are!

189
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,100
Mother,

190
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:06,700
please put them on.

191
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:09,490
What?

192
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,850
Exactly, Mother.

193
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,370
You debuted at 10 years old,

194
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,900
and Hua Mulan was your signature act.

195
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:20,340
If you hadn't got married,

196
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,460
you might have become
a famous opera star by now.

197
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:23,980
- Come on.
- Yes!

198
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:25,420
Feast our eyes.

199
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:26,580
No.

200
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:28,620
I'm too old to perform now.

201
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:29,700
Mother,

202
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:31,220
you always say

203
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:33,580
you looked utterly gorgeous on stage.

204
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:35,460
Those days performing

205
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,020
were when you felt happiest

206
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:39,660
and most at ease in your entire life.

207
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,460
Let's revisit those memories today!

208
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:43,860
No, I can't.

209
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:45,140
I forgot how to perform.

210
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:46,020
- Mother.
- Mother.

211
00:08:46,020 --> 00:08:47,980
No, my voice just won't cooperate.

212
00:08:47,980 --> 00:08:49,100
Look!

213
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:50,620
No outsiders are here today.

214
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:52,460
Just perform for us.

215
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,020
Exactly!

216
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:53,780
Yes.

217
00:08:54,060 --> 00:08:55,900
I also want to watch you
perform Hua Mulan.

218
00:08:55,980 --> 00:08:57,140
So do I.

219
00:08:57,260 --> 00:08:58,620
Please, Grandma!

220
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:05,300
Alright then.

221
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:07,140
I'll perform.

222
00:09:30,660 --> 00:09:32,060
Mulan.

223
00:09:33,060 --> 00:09:34,820
Mulan.

224
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:39,220
Brother.

225
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:44,780
Seeing you lost in thought alone here,

226
00:09:45,060 --> 00:09:50,500
I wonder what troubles your heart.

227
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:55,380
When I just saw the distant moon,

228
00:09:55,780 --> 00:09:58,420
my heart turned homeward

229
00:09:58,420 --> 00:10:00,740
to elders, neighbors,

230
00:10:00,780 --> 00:10:04,420
brothers and sisters.

231
00:10:04,420 --> 00:10:05,340
To the head table!

232
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:08,140
Wait a moment.

233
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:08,860
Let me check first.

234
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:12,420
Okay, push carefully.

235
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:15,380
Come over here!

236
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:34,540
Excellent!

237
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:36,780
Marvelous!

238
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:39,860
Here!

239
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,380
Grandma, you performed beautifully!

240
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:44,180
Mother.

241
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,020
Old age has taken its toll.

242
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,980
I can't perform as I did before.

243
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:50,540
Wonderful, Mother.

244
00:10:51,820 --> 00:10:54,020
How does it feel to perform
on stage again?

245
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:56,900
I feel like

246
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:59,260
I've returned to my younger days.

247
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:00,980
Mother,

248
00:11:02,020 --> 00:11:02,780
are you happy?

249
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:03,860
Yes.

250
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:06,940
Today is my happiest day

251
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,300
in the past 60 years!

252
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:11,980
So good to hear.

253
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:16,420
Do you know

254
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:18,060
who arranged all of this?

255
00:11:19,540 --> 00:11:20,260
Who?

256
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:24,140
Everything today,

257
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,820
like booking the hall,
hiring the opera troupe,

258
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:28,220
customizing the costumes,

259
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:33,460
was meticulously planned by Chu Shaohua.

260
00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:35,420
She said

261
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:37,500
you've spent your life
working for our family,

262
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:39,500
for me and for Yuan,

263
00:11:40,060 --> 00:11:41,620
with scarcely a moment's rest.

264
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:43,300
So she insisted

265
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,780
on helping you reclaim

266
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:47,140
the happiest moments of your life

267
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:48,020
on your 60th birthday.

268
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:52,940
Where is she now?

269
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:55,980
We booked a birthday banquet nearby.

270
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:57,700
She should be busy over there.

271
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:00,340
Let's go

272
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:02,020
see her.

273
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:08,420
Madam, congratulations!

274
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:09,100
Thank you.

275
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:10,140
- Thank you.
- Congratulations!

276
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:11,420
Please have a seat.

277
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:12,340
Please.

278
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:13,580
Madam.

279
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:15,220
We're here to share in your blessings.

280
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:16,340
Many thanks!

281
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:16,900
Congratulations!

282
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:17,980
Thank you all so much!

283
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:18,860
Congratulations!

284
00:12:18,900 --> 00:12:20,100
Thanks. Please take your seats.

285
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:23,060
Thanks.

286
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:24,060
Congratulations!

287
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:24,980
Many thanks!

288
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:27,140
Let's go.

289
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:30,860
Prepare the wine.

290
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:31,780
Move faster.

291
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:37,140
Madam.

292
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:42,340
Shaohua,

293
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:44,380
you've worked hard.

294
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:46,140
Not at all.

295
00:12:48,340 --> 00:12:49,460
The journey

296
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:51,140
hasn't been easy, right?

297
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:55,020
Everything turned out well.

298
00:12:56,620 --> 00:12:57,420
Xia Chu.

299
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:02,580
Your life with Xia Chu

300
00:13:02,820 --> 00:13:04,940
will keep getting better.

301
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:07,220
Mother,

302
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:09,380
do you approve of our marriage?

303
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:12,060
As long as you two feel it's right,

304
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:14,140
don't worry about what others say.

305
00:13:14,540 --> 00:13:16,420
As long as you find joy in each other,

306
00:13:16,580 --> 00:13:17,940
nothing else matters.

307
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:20,260
Madam,

308
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:21,980
thank you.

309
00:13:22,940 --> 00:13:26,220
Don't mention it.
Today I should be thanking you.

310
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:30,420
If you want to keep making me happy,

311
00:13:30,420 --> 00:13:31,940
get married already

312
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:34,380
and give me lots of grandchildren!

313
00:13:35,460 --> 00:13:37,980
Once the Chinese Nationalist Army
liberates Shanghai,

314
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:38,980
we'll get married.

315
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:41,700
How long will that take?

316
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:43,180
Soon.

317
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:56,400
[Year 1927]
[Welcome the Chinese Nationalist Army]

318
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:11,420
Given the momentum
of the Chinese Nationalist Army,

319
00:14:11,620 --> 00:14:13,340
China's reunification
seems imminent!

320
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:17,580
So Xia Chu was right about this.

321
00:14:19,220 --> 00:14:21,260
Among those who studied
in Japan back then,

322
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:23,420
he showed
the sharpest political insight.

323
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:28,180
Seems my decision
to let him pursue politics

324
00:14:28,700 --> 00:14:29,660
was a winning gamble.

325
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:33,340
Please sign the budget

326
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:35,340
of the morale-boosting team.

327
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:52,020
Let's go to the celebration welcoming
the Chinese Nationalist Army

328
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:53,820
by various sectors of Shanghai.

329
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:56,780
Okay.

330
00:14:58,900 --> 00:14:59,460
Zhiqiu.

331
00:15:10,620 --> 00:15:13,420
Xia Chu and Ms. Chu are preparing for
their wedding.

332
00:15:16,500 --> 00:15:17,260
Congratulations.

333
00:15:19,980 --> 00:15:22,020
I thought highly of you paired with her.

334
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:25,140
Never expected fate had other plans.

335
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,540
I hope this won't affect

336
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:28,700
our future collaboration.

337
00:15:30,820 --> 00:15:31,380
Don't worry.

338
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:33,740
I never hold grudges against money.

339
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:45,200
[Tong Tong Dress Shop]

340
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:46,140
Mr. Xia,

341
00:15:46,380 --> 00:15:47,380
if it doesn't fit,

342
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:48,260
please let me know.

343
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:48,900
Thank you.

344
00:15:59,660 --> 00:16:00,380
How do I look?

345
00:16:06,140 --> 00:16:06,780
Absolutely stunning.

346
00:16:13,340 --> 00:16:14,860
It feels like a dream.

347
00:16:15,780 --> 00:16:19,740
♪Your voice drifts to me,
never near, never far♪

348
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:20,660
More beautiful than a dream.

349
00:16:22,100 --> 00:16:27,060
♪Photo curled inside my worn wallet♪

350
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:29,460
After so many years,

351
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:32,020
I can finally marry you.

352
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:36,860
♪As seasons shift and fade♪

353
00:16:36,860 --> 00:16:38,100
We're finally together.

354
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:42,380
We'll never part again.

355
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:45,260
♪See the leaf fall at my toe♪

356
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:48,500
Excuse me.

357
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:50,900
♪Like time quietly slipping away♪

358
00:16:51,220 --> 00:16:53,300
Ms. Chu,
would you like to try on this qipao?

359
00:16:53,300 --> 00:16:55,540
♪And I couldn't quite understand♪

360
00:16:55,540 --> 00:16:56,900
But I have this wedding dress.

361
00:16:58,260 --> 00:16:59,260
The wedding dress is for the ceremony,

362
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:01,100
and a qipao is for the banquet.

363
00:17:01,660 --> 00:17:02,460
Try it on.

364
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:05,180
Haven't seen you in a red qipao.

365
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:06,220
Okay.

366
00:17:06,220 --> 00:17:08,300
♪We walk through ordinary days♪

367
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,100
Alright, here.

368
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:12,300
Miss, this way please.

369
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:12,780
Okay.

370
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:14,900
♪What remains flows like rivers wide♪

371
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:15,620
Mr. Xia.

372
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:20,420
♪Who will hold the tears
we used to hide?♪

373
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:22,580
Shaohua, something urgent came up.

374
00:17:22,580 --> 00:17:23,580
I need to deal with it now.

375
00:17:23,860 --> 00:17:24,740
I'll leave first.

376
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:26,460
Head home after trying on the qipao.

377
00:17:26,460 --> 00:17:27,980
What's so urgent?

378
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:28,980
I'll come to you once I'm done.

379
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:42,940
Ms. Chu,

380
00:17:45,020 --> 00:17:45,900
Mr. Xia…

381
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:49,660
He has left.

382
00:17:52,740 --> 00:17:53,340
Ms. Chu,

383
00:17:54,020 --> 00:17:55,980
you look stunning in this outfit.

384
00:20:23,340 --> 00:20:24,140
Shaohua.

385
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:40,120
[Morgue]

386
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:12,240
[Nurse Station]

387
00:21:17,860 --> 00:21:18,900
You're awake.

388
00:21:24,940 --> 00:21:26,220
I'm at the hospital now?

389
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,500
You passed out,

390
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:30,700
and we sent you here.

391
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:34,860
Be careful.

392
00:21:35,260 --> 00:21:36,580
What's the date today?

393
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:38,380
It's the 14th.

394
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:42,900
What are you doing?

395
00:21:43,540 --> 00:21:45,140
The wedding is in two days.

396
00:21:45,140 --> 00:21:46,540
Many details to be finalized.

397
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:47,340
Shaohua.

398
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:52,060
Xia Chu...

399
00:21:54,780 --> 00:21:55,540
I understand.

400
00:21:57,580 --> 00:21:58,580
He's busy.

401
00:21:59,220 --> 00:22:00,380
We agreed

402
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:02,740
I'll take charge of the wedding.

403
00:22:02,780 --> 00:22:04,220
He just needs to show up for it.

404
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:10,860
Why are you also here?

405
00:22:11,380 --> 00:22:12,900
He's been here for a day and a night.

406
00:22:13,580 --> 00:22:14,620
I thought you were busy.

407
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:17,100
Aren't you managing Wen's Pharmacy?

408
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:35,500
Hello, Dahua Hotel?

409
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,260
Yes.

410
00:22:36,460 --> 00:22:38,860
This is Chu Shaohua.
My wedding is on the 16th.

411
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:43,740
Could I add two extra tables

412
00:22:43,860 --> 00:22:44,540
of banquet dishes?

413
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:48,020
Okay. Thank you.

414
00:22:58,340 --> 00:22:59,420
Hello, flower shop?

415
00:23:00,540 --> 00:23:01,460
This is Chu Shaohua.

416
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:02,900
I want to confirm

417
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:05,700
if the flowers for my wedding are ready.

418
00:23:07,260 --> 00:23:08,580
I see. Thank you.

419
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:11,700
Enough.

420
00:23:16,060 --> 00:23:17,540
Are you really that free?

421
00:23:18,260 --> 00:23:19,260
If yes,

422
00:23:19,540 --> 00:23:20,780
go pick up my wedding cakes

423
00:23:21,260 --> 00:23:21,980
at Caizhi Pastry Shop.

424
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:23,380
Shaohua.

425
00:23:24,820 --> 00:23:25,820
There's no wedding.

426
00:23:26,460 --> 00:23:27,100
Erniu,

427
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:30,100
I should pick up my resized ring.

428
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:32,260
Would you come with me?

429
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:33,420
Let's go.

430
00:23:37,860 --> 00:23:39,180
What's wrong with her?

431
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:20,820
[Wedding Invitation]

432
00:24:51,940 --> 00:24:52,620
Mrs. Xia.

433
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:57,020
Where's Mr. Xia?

434
00:24:59,460 --> 00:25:01,020
He's handling Xia Chu's funeral.

435
00:25:03,380 --> 00:25:03,980
My condolences.

436
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:06,740
How is Madam doing?

437
00:25:08,140 --> 00:25:09,220
She's at the hospital now.

438
00:25:09,740 --> 00:25:12,580
Youze and Youwen
are keeping her company.

439
00:25:22,060 --> 00:25:23,660
What's going on with Shaohua?

440
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:26,700
She's still preparing for the wedding.

441
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:28,980
She refuses to accept the fact.

442
00:25:30,100 --> 00:25:31,100
No matter how hard we tried

443
00:25:31,100 --> 00:25:31,740
to convince her,

444
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:33,540
she refused to believe it.

445
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:35,340
That's why we asked you here.

446
00:25:36,740 --> 00:25:38,300
You're part of the Xia family.

447
00:25:38,700 --> 00:25:39,860
She may believe what you say.

448
00:26:01,780 --> 00:26:02,460
Shaohua.

449
00:26:05,300 --> 00:26:05,980
Oh,

450
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:07,540
you came just in time.

451
00:26:08,420 --> 00:26:10,660
Help me check tomorrow's wedding menu.

452
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:14,580
Shaohua,

453
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,340
stop.

454
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:19,500
There won't be a wedding tomorrow.

455
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,300
Xia Chu

456
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:24,460
is gone.

457
00:26:27,580 --> 00:26:28,540
Where did he go?

458
00:26:28,780 --> 00:26:30,260
He's not coming back.

459
00:26:32,260 --> 00:26:33,140
Impossible.

460
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:34,660
I believe he will.

461
00:26:37,020 --> 00:26:37,700
Shaohua,

462
00:26:38,580 --> 00:26:39,460
listen to me.

463
00:26:41,620 --> 00:26:43,420
Xia Chu is dead.

464
00:26:53,140 --> 00:26:54,780
He will come back to life.

465
00:26:55,860 --> 00:26:57,740
No one can come back to life.

466
00:26:57,940 --> 00:26:59,020
But Xia Chu can.

467
00:26:59,820 --> 00:27:02,060
Once we heard nothing
from him for years.

468
00:27:02,540 --> 00:27:04,260
We assumed he might be dead,

469
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:06,620
held a funeral for him,

470
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:08,340
even erected a tombstone.

471
00:27:09,180 --> 00:27:09,980
Yet what happened in the end?

472
00:27:10,620 --> 00:27:11,780
He came back alive.

473
00:27:16,380 --> 00:27:17,580
This time, he's really gone.

474
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,460
He did die.

475
00:27:24,020 --> 00:27:24,700
Now,

476
00:27:25,260 --> 00:27:26,100
stop crying.

477
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:27,780
Rest assured.

478
00:27:29,060 --> 00:27:30,500
He'll come tomorrow.

479
00:27:31,460 --> 00:27:33,540
He'll be there on time for the wedding.

480
00:27:45,780 --> 00:27:46,940
This wedding dress is so beautiful.

481
00:27:50,180 --> 00:27:50,860
It's perfect.

482
00:27:52,220 --> 00:27:54,900
Tomorrow is my wedding day with Xia Chu.

483
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:07,060
Shhh, stop crying.

484
00:28:07,060 --> 00:28:08,500
I know you don't want to part with me.

485
00:28:09,540 --> 00:28:10,100
Erniu,

486
00:28:10,940 --> 00:28:11,940
don't worry.

487
00:28:12,740 --> 00:28:14,700
Even after I get married,

488
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:17,020
we'll still see each other.

489
00:28:17,340 --> 00:28:18,820
We remain best friends.

490
00:28:21,020 --> 00:28:22,300
Best friends for life.

491
00:28:26,340 --> 00:28:27,260
Do you know

492
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:31,420
how many years I've waited for this day?

493
00:28:34,060 --> 00:28:35,020
Eleven years.

494
00:28:38,060 --> 00:28:38,740
I know.

495
00:28:42,420 --> 00:28:43,180
Go to sleep.

496
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:44,180
Sleep.

497
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:46,740
Get some good rest.

498
00:28:47,940 --> 00:28:48,500
Alright.

499
00:28:48,660 --> 00:28:50,100
Get some sleep, too.

500
00:28:51,260 --> 00:28:52,820
Let's sleep.

501
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:56,380
Have a lovely dream.

502
00:28:56,380 --> 00:29:00,780
Tomorrow will be my wedding day.

503
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:40,660
Shaohua?

504
00:29:57,420 --> 00:29:58,540
I'd like to use the phone.

505
00:29:58,700 --> 00:29:59,380
Come in, please.

506
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:08,470
♪A blanket lying on the snow♪

507
00:30:09,110 --> 00:30:14,590
♪Melting frost in silent glow♪

508
00:30:15,430 --> 00:30:18,350
♪On endless snowy roads, I roam♪

509
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:21,070
♪Seeking the shore within my soul♪

510
00:30:21,870 --> 00:30:28,510
♪Winds howl wild, my soul, near torn♪

511
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:31,500
Where are you going?

512
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:32,500
I'm going to Xia Chu.

513
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:33,340
He's dead.

514
00:30:33,540 --> 00:30:34,420
You're lying!

515
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:36,020
He was shot five times.

516
00:30:36,020 --> 00:30:36,940
Three bullets hit his chest!

517
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:39,340
No! He's waiting for me at Dahua Hotel!

518
00:30:39,340 --> 00:30:40,700
All of us have seen his body,

519
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:41,300
including you.

520
00:30:41,580 --> 00:30:43,300
Today is my joyful wedding day with him!

521
00:30:43,300 --> 00:30:44,460
It's the day they lay him to rest!

522
00:30:44,460 --> 00:30:45,340
Let go of me!

523
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:46,900
The auspicious moment is nearly here!

524
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:47,780
The ceremony begins soon!

525
00:30:47,780 --> 00:30:48,300
Shaohua.

526
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:50,340
If I don't go now, it'll be too late!

527
00:30:50,580 --> 00:30:52,420
Xia Chu!

528
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:54,260
Chu Shaohua, pull yourself together!

529
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:57,860
Look at what you've become!

530
00:30:58,740 --> 00:31:00,140
You're letting me down!

531
00:31:02,260 --> 00:31:04,180
You refused to back down

532
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:05,100
to any challenges.

533
00:31:05,780 --> 00:31:07,460
You clearly know what happened,

534
00:31:08,340 --> 00:31:09,980
yet you chose to act like a coward,

535
00:31:10,500 --> 00:31:11,700
a frightened little rabbit.

536
00:31:12,860 --> 00:31:14,220
You picked running away instead.

537
00:31:14,620 --> 00:31:15,220
No.

538
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:16,660
You are a coward.

539
00:31:17,460 --> 00:31:18,220
I'm not.

540
00:31:18,820 --> 00:31:19,620
I'm not.

541
00:31:19,820 --> 00:31:21,020
Then face the reality.

542
00:31:21,020 --> 00:31:22,580
♪Fate, day by day♪

543
00:31:22,580 --> 00:31:23,500
♪Earnest and brave♪

544
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,660
♪Leaves no regrets♪

545
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:25,700
Xia Chu is dead.

546
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:28,700
♪Dawn, bit by bit♪

547
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:29,820
♪Glorious and scorching♪

548
00:31:29,820 --> 00:31:31,220
♪No longer alone♪

549
00:31:31,220 --> 00:31:32,380
Xia Chu is dead?

550
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:36,820
♪Flames light the way
where despair once lay♪

551
00:31:37,140 --> 00:31:40,300
♪I shield you, my very soul entwined♪

552
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,340
He is dead.

553
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:47,540
♪Through hardship, to the goal♪

554
00:31:47,540 --> 00:31:49,900
♪We reach, at last♪

555
00:31:49,900 --> 00:31:51,340
♪The shore we hold fast♪

556
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:54,140
Xia Chu!

557
00:32:11,320 --> 00:32:13,480
[Grave]

558
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:37,100
I've found the murderer of Xia Chu.

559
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:39,700
Who is it?

560
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:41,620
Mu Ziru.

561
00:32:45,020 --> 00:32:46,220
He's as good as dead.

562
00:32:55,050 --> 00:32:58,440
[Grave of My Brother Xia Chu]

563
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:13,320
[Spring Garden Restaurant]

564
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:39,940
What would you like to eat today?

565
00:34:44,260 --> 00:34:45,700
What special occasion is it today?

566
00:34:46,140 --> 00:34:47,100
Unusually romantic.

567
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:49,260
I've made every day romantic.

568
00:34:58,500 --> 00:34:59,340
Oilie?

569
00:35:00,100 --> 00:35:00,900
Do you like it?

570
00:35:04,780 --> 00:35:05,660
You've struck it rich?

571
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:09,540
Both making money and getting promoted.

572
00:35:10,060 --> 00:35:11,180
If I wear this out,

573
00:35:11,620 --> 00:35:13,620
it'll blind everyone with its shine.

574
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:16,380
Heavens!

575
00:35:17,620 --> 00:35:18,900
I love you so much, Mu.

576
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:23,020
If you love me, marry me.

577
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:27,260
Are you proposing to me?

578
00:35:28,420 --> 00:35:28,980
Look.

579
00:35:29,900 --> 00:35:31,540
We've been together for years.

580
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:33,660
I should start a family at my age.

581
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:35,700
Plus, my master will switch professions.

582
00:35:35,780 --> 00:35:37,660
I won't deal with violence anymore.

583
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:44,260
I just want a peaceful life with you.

584
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:48,100
Will you marry me?

585
00:35:51,140 --> 00:35:51,820
Shaohua.

586
00:35:54,020 --> 00:35:54,580
Look.

587
00:35:58,140 --> 00:35:59,180
What are you doing?

588
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:01,660
Ms. Chu,

589
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:03,620
what do you mean by this?

590
00:36:03,980 --> 00:36:05,020
You killed Xia Chu.

591
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:07,540
What are you talking about?

592
00:36:08,140 --> 00:36:09,220
Drop the act, Mr. Mu.

593
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:11,060
Who started the rumor?

594
00:36:11,580 --> 00:36:12,340
Shaohua,

595
00:36:13,220 --> 00:36:14,500
are you sure?

596
00:36:15,180 --> 00:36:17,020
Fine. Then tell me.

597
00:36:17,940 --> 00:36:19,580
How did you get promoted

598
00:36:20,180 --> 00:36:22,260
and get that large bonus?

599
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:23,420
Who told you?

600
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:26,100
If you don't want anyone to know,

601
00:36:26,580 --> 00:36:27,700
better not do it at all.

602
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:28,780
Don't shoot!

603
00:36:29,500 --> 00:36:30,060
Misunderstanding!

604
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:31,300
Xia Chu is dead!

605
00:36:31,620 --> 00:36:32,580
The gun went off accidentally.

606
00:36:32,860 --> 00:36:33,540
I swear,

607
00:36:34,300 --> 00:36:35,220
I didn't mean to fire the gun.

608
00:36:35,220 --> 00:36:36,500
He has five bullet holes in him.

609
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:38,540
All from stray bullets?

610
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:39,820
It was chaotic back then.

611
00:36:39,980 --> 00:36:41,300
When shots rang out,
everyone started firing.

612
00:36:41,860 --> 00:36:43,220
It was impossible to tell who was who.

613
00:36:43,620 --> 00:36:44,500
It really was you?

614
00:36:44,540 --> 00:36:45,660
I was carrying out an operation.

615
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:47,820
I swear, he wasn't my target.

616
00:36:48,100 --> 00:36:48,820
Besides,

617
00:36:48,860 --> 00:36:49,940
He wasn't on the list.

618
00:36:49,980 --> 00:36:51,420
He suddenly showed up there.

619
00:36:51,460 --> 00:36:52,700
But you shot.

620
00:36:53,060 --> 00:36:53,980
Someone was shouting

621
00:36:54,020 --> 00:36:54,740
that someone resisted arrest.

622
00:36:56,220 --> 00:36:57,700
I just shot before thinking.

623
00:36:58,260 --> 00:36:59,900
I didn't know that person was Xia Chu.

624
00:37:00,420 --> 00:37:01,900
Three shots in a row!

625
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:04,660
He was on the ground,

626
00:37:04,660 --> 00:37:06,060
yet you added two more bullets.

627
00:37:08,980 --> 00:37:10,580
You did kill him?

628
00:37:13,620 --> 00:37:14,340
Shaohua,

629
00:37:16,060 --> 00:37:17,740
I was out of my mind.

630
00:37:18,100 --> 00:37:19,780
I had no idea what I did.

631
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:23,020
I regret it deeply now.

632
00:37:23,060 --> 00:37:23,980
Regret?

633
00:37:24,700 --> 00:37:25,420
Mr. Mu,

634
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:28,180
you said at the victory banquet

635
00:37:28,660 --> 00:37:30,780
that if you had known
killing communists paid so well,

636
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:32,740
you'd have killed several more.

637
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:34,340
I know

638
00:37:35,420 --> 00:37:36,700
it won't help to say anything now.

639
00:37:37,020 --> 00:37:39,580
For the sake of your bond with Erniu,

640
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:41,140
give me a chance to atone.

641
00:37:41,540 --> 00:37:42,500
You can set any conditions.

642
00:37:42,780 --> 00:37:44,340
I will absolutely do

643
00:37:45,020 --> 00:37:45,820
whatever I can.

644
00:37:45,860 --> 00:37:47,100
Don't drag us into this.

645
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:49,540
If you want to negotiate terms,

646
00:37:50,620 --> 00:37:51,860
go talk to Xia Chu.

647
00:37:52,220 --> 00:37:53,580
If he forgives you,

648
00:37:54,460 --> 00:37:55,580
I have no objection.

649
00:37:55,580 --> 00:37:56,220
No!

650
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:57,900
Erniu, step aside!

651
00:37:58,100 --> 00:37:59,460
No, don't shoot!

652
00:37:59,580 --> 00:38:00,180
Step aside!

653
00:38:00,940 --> 00:38:01,780
Xia Chu is dead.

654
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:03,580
I must avenge him!

655
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:04,420
I know,

656
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:06,140
but I'm begging you.

657
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:07,700
Don't shoot!

658
00:38:11,580 --> 00:38:12,100
Go!

659
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:24,580
Put down the gun!

660
00:38:24,740 --> 00:38:26,700
She nearly killed me.

661
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:28,340
Put down the gun!

662
00:38:28,380 --> 00:38:29,100
Get out!

663
00:38:32,580 --> 00:38:33,340
Mu Ziru,

664
00:38:33,980 --> 00:38:35,060
if you dare shoot,

665
00:38:36,580 --> 00:38:38,300
I promise you'll never see me again

666
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:39,580
as long as you live.

667
00:38:39,700 --> 00:38:40,300
You…

668
00:38:40,580 --> 00:38:41,260
Erniu.

669
00:38:42,940 --> 00:38:43,780
Everyone's here?

670
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,340
Wen Zhiqiu.

671
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:51,100
Mu,

672
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,700
let me tell you straight.

673
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:53,860
It's utterly unchivalrous

674
00:38:53,860 --> 00:38:55,620
by pointing a gun at a woman.

675
00:38:55,620 --> 00:38:56,340
Don't move!

676
00:38:58,740 --> 00:38:59,420
Mr. Mu.

677
00:39:04,980 --> 00:39:05,900
And you, Erniu.

678
00:39:06,260 --> 00:39:07,460
Guns aren't toys.

679
00:39:07,780 --> 00:39:08,460
Put it down.

680
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:12,900
None of your business. Leave now.

681
00:39:13,100 --> 00:39:14,780
But we agreed to watch a film together.

682
00:39:15,660 --> 00:39:16,620
Do you think

683
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:19,580
you can come and go whenever you please?

684
00:39:20,260 --> 00:39:20,900
Fine.

685
00:39:21,780 --> 00:39:22,860
Then nobody is leaving.

686
00:39:30,060 --> 00:39:30,820
You may go,

687
00:39:31,460 --> 00:39:32,420
but she stays.

688
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:33,540
That won't do.

689
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:35,300
I bought two tickets.

690
00:39:35,620 --> 00:39:36,660
If she won't come with me,

691
00:39:36,660 --> 00:39:37,620
will you watch it with me?

692
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:40,100
Come on, darling.

693
00:39:40,420 --> 00:39:41,260
Let's go watch a movie.

694
00:39:47,740 --> 00:39:48,500
Go!

695
00:39:59,820 --> 00:40:00,460
Go.

696
00:40:11,860 --> 00:40:12,700
- Chase.
- Come back!

697
00:40:19,260 --> 00:40:20,260
Shaohua and I

698
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:23,100
are soul sisters forged in the fires
of growing up together.

699
00:40:23,900 --> 00:40:25,340
For a man like you…

700
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:39,680
[Jiangyue Hall]

701
00:40:44,460 --> 00:40:45,660
I know you treat me well.

702
00:40:46,340 --> 00:40:47,820
I'll repay you double someday.

703
00:40:51,260 --> 00:40:52,060
Mu Ziru,

704
00:40:55,860 --> 00:40:57,180
there's no future for us.

705
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:58,420
What do you mean?

706
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:00,900
I saved your life today.

707
00:41:03,540 --> 00:41:04,540
Let's call it square

708
00:41:05,460 --> 00:41:07,420
after all these years of your kindness.

709
00:41:08,580 --> 00:41:09,540
From now on,

710
00:41:10,380 --> 00:41:11,620
we go our separate ways.

711
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:12,620
Why?

712
00:41:13,140 --> 00:41:14,260
You killed Xia Chu.

713
00:41:16,540 --> 00:41:18,100
If I stay with you,

714
00:41:19,500 --> 00:41:20,980
it's a betrayal to Shaohua.

715
00:41:23,300 --> 00:41:24,900
Can't believe you'd dump me

716
00:41:24,900 --> 00:41:25,980
for some random guy!

717
00:41:26,500 --> 00:41:27,820
You don't know

718
00:41:29,660 --> 00:41:31,860
what Xia Chu meant to Shaohua.

719
00:41:38,980 --> 00:41:39,900
From now on,

720
00:41:42,340 --> 00:41:43,780
