724
00:41:50,580 --> 00:41:51,860
Better pray for yourself.

725
00:42:07,580 --> 00:42:08,380
Give me back my gun.

726
00:42:19,380 --> 00:42:21,060
How did you know I took it?

727
00:42:22,380 --> 00:42:23,260
Only you

728
00:42:23,260 --> 00:42:24,500
