730
00:42:27,500 --> 00:42:28,220
I'm sorry.

731
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:31,580
Come on. What were you thinking?

732
00:42:31,940 --> 00:42:33,860
Didn't let me perish
alongside Wang Guodong.

733
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:35,500
Yet you came to Mu Ziru

734
00:42:35,660 --> 00:42:36,580
