735
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:39,740
Are you crazy?

736
00:42:45,060 --> 00:42:46,700
I just wanted to avenge Xia Chu.

737
00:42:46,740 --> 00:42:47,740
By using a stupid method?

738
00:42:50,180 --> 00:42:51,300
Where's your shrewdness?

739
00:42:52,020 --> 00:42:52,940
Your judgment?

